text: twice package especially used running repeat analyzing transposable elements transcription factors. Functions downstream analysis TEKRABber results: 1. ensIDtoName(): transform ensembl ID gene name human readability. 2. kznfsComplexHeatmap(): plot KRAB-ZNFs heatmap taking input TEKRABber using ComplexHeatmap package. 3. teComplexHeatmap(): similar kznfsComplexHeatmap() transposable elements. 4. pieTE(): visualize abundance transposable elements class level using pie chart. 5. saveTErmsk(): subset rmsk GTF file (class, family, gene) save rda file. 6. rmskFilter(): filter subfamily, subclass repeatmasker annotation files downstream analysis.
